        section.section.faq__section
            .section__container
                h3.section__heading--secondary.center.capitalize frequenty asked questions
                .faq__accordion
                    .faq__accordion--item
                        .accordion__content--title
                            h3.accordion__heading What is clubmerce?
                            span &minus;
                        .faq__accordion--content
                            p.accordion__content--text Clubmerce is an innovative affiliate marketing platform that connects brands, vendors, and affiliate marketers in a seamless ecosystem. With Clubmerce, affiliates can promote a wide range of products and services while earning commissions on successful product purchase.
                    .faq__accordion--item
                        .accordion__content--title
                            h3.accordion__heading What types of products can I promote as an affiliate?
                            span &minus;
                        .faq__accordion--content
                            p.accordion__content--text As an affiliate, you can promote a diverse range of products or services including physical products, digital products, services, travel and hospitality, beauty and personal care, financial products, home and garden items, food and beverage products, fashion and accessories, and lifestyle and wellness products.
                    .faq__accordion--item
                        .accordion__content--title
                            h3.accordion__heading Is there a minimum payout threshold for affiliate earnings?
                            span &minus;
                        .faq__accordion--content
                            p.accordion__content--text The minimum payout threshold for affiliate earnings on Clubmerce is $50. Once your earnings reach this threshold, you become eligible for withdrawal. This ensures that you receive a substantial amount before initiating the payout process. Clubmerce values your efforts as an affiliate and aims to provide a fair and transparent system for earning commissions.
                    .faq__accordion--item
                        .accordion__content--title
                            h3.accordion__heading Can I promote multiple products from different vendors on this platform?
                            span &minus;
                        .faq__accordion--content
                            p.accordion__content--text Yes, on Clubmerce, you have the flexibility to promote multiple products or services from different vendors within the platform. As an affiliate, you can explore a diverse marketplace and choose from a wide range of offerings. This allows you to diversify your promotional efforts, target various niches, and cater to the interests of your audience. Clubmerce provides a centralized platform where you can easily manage and track your promotions across different vendors, making it convenient to engage with multiple products or services simultaneously.
                    .faq__accordion--item
                        .accordion__content--title
                            h3.accordion__heading How can I maximize my affiliate marketing success on this platform?
                            span &minus;
                        .faq__accordion--content
                            p.accordion__content--text To maximize your affiliate marketing success on Clubmerce, consider implementing the following strategies:

                            p.accordion__content--text 1. Choose the Right Products: Select products or services that align with your target audience's interests and needs.

                            p.accordion__content--text 2. Build a Strong Online Presence: Establish a compelling online presence through a website, blog, or social media channels.

                            p.accordion__content--text 3. Leverage Promotional Tools: Utilize the marketing tools and resources provided by Clubmerce, such as banners, text links, and product widgets.

                            p.accordion__content--text 4. Engage Your Audience: Interact with your audience through engaging content, comments, and social media engagement.

                            p.accordion__content--text 5. Track and Analyze Performance: Regularly monitor your affiliate performance using Clubmerce's tracking and analytics tools.
